              p(class="text-xs text-black lg:text-sm") 從生日、紀念日、情人節到聖誕節，送禮始終是伴侶間的默契大考驗，誠摯推薦 5 款實⽤與樂趣兼具的贈禮，讓送禮成為關係中的潤滑劑！從生日、紀念日、情人節到聖誕節，送禮始終是伴侶間的默契大考驗，誠摯推薦 
              p(class="text-xs text-black lg:text-sm") 從生日、紀念日、情人節到聖誕節，送禮始終是伴侶間的默契大考驗，誠摯推薦 5 款實⽤與樂趣兼具的贈禮，讓送禮成為關係中的潤滑劑！
          div(class="flex-1 max-w-[352px] w-full h-full lg:mt-0 mt-10")
            div(class="flex lg:flex-col flex-row lg:max-h-[548px] w-full h-full lg:p-4 lg:border lg:rounded lg:border-slate-200")
              div(class="relative")
                img(class="lg:max-w-[320px] max-w-[114px] lg:max-h-[400px] max-h-[136px] w-full h-full object-cover" src="./images/index/planning2.png", alt="")
                button(class="absolute lg:top-[15px] top-2 lg:right-3 right-2")
                  img(class="w-3 h-3 lg:w-5 lg:h-5" src="./images/main/like.svg", alt="")
              div(class="flex flex-col flex-1 ml-4 lg:ml-0")
