                p(class="text-base text-black lg:mt-3 mt-[6px]") 聖誕節慶麵包與橄欖油套組
                div(class="flex flex-col mt-3 space-y-2 lg:space-x-6 lg:space-y-0 lg:flex-row lg:mt-10")
